Photo by Instapray on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '"Cast all your anxiety on Him because He cares for you." 1 Peter 5:7'.

Photo by Instapray on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '"Do not be anxious about anything, but in every situation, by prayer and petition, with thanksgiving, present your requests to God." Philippians 4:6'.

Photo by Instapray on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '"Peace I leave with you; my peace I give you. I do not give to you as the world gives. Do not let your hearts be troubled and do not be afraid." John 14:27'.
Photo by Instapray on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '"For the Spirit God gave us does not make us timid, but gives us power, love and self-discipline." 2 Timothy 1:7'.

Photo by Instapray on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '"When I am afraid, I put my trust in you. In God, whose word I praise- in God I trust and am not afraid. What can mere mortals do to me?" Psalms 56:3-4'.
